      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Marc Schoenauer</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:251px;\"><a href=\"https://www.lri.fr/~marc/\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/3/3d/Marc-schoenauer.jpg\" width=\"249\" height=\"273\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Marc-schoenauer.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Marc Schoenauer <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Marc Schoenauer</b>,<br />\na French mathematician and computer scientist, along with <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> head of the <i>TAO Project Team</i> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> \nand senior researcher of <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Laboratory_for_Computer_Science_(University_of_Paris-Sud)\">LRI</a> with <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/National_Institute_for_Research_in_Computer_Science_and_Control\">INRIA</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Saclay\">Saclay</a>-<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%8Ele-de-France_%28region%29\">IDF</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/French_National_Centre_for_Scientific_Research\">CNRS</a>, <a href=\"/University_of_Paris#11\" title=\"University of Paris\">Paris-Sud 11 University</a>. \nHe graduated at <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%89cole_Normale_Sup%C3%A9rieure\">École Normale Supérieure</a> in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paris\">Paris</a>, and obtained a Ph.D. in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Numerical_analysis\">numerical analysis</a> at <a href=\"/University_of_Paris#6\" title=\"University of Paris\">Université Paris 6</a> in 1980. \nSchoenauer has been working in the field of <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming#EvolutionaryComputation\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">evolutionary computation</a> (EC) and <a href=\"/Genetic_Programming\" title=\"Genetic Programming\">genetic programming</a> since the early 90s, more particularly at the interface between EC and <a href=\"/Learning\" title=\"Learning\">machine learning</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Selected_Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Selected Publications</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#1990_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">1990 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2000_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2000 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2010_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2010 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1.4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Publications\">Selected Publications</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Publications\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"1990_...\">1990 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: 1990 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>1990</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/B9781558601413500109\">Incremental Learning of Rules and Meta-rules</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/icml/ml1990.html\">ML 1990</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> (<b>1992</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/2283004_Learning_to_Control_Inconsistent_Knowledge\">Learning to Control Inconsistent Knowledge</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ecai/ecai92.html\">ECAI 1992</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://recherche.enac.fr/~delahaye/\">Daniel Delahaye</a>, <a href=\"/Jean-Marc_Alliot\" title=\"Jean-Marc Alliot\">Jean-Marc Alliot</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=H2VjSOgAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Jean-Loup Farges</a> (<b>1994</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.researchgate.net/publication/2489370_Genetic_Algorithms_for_Air_Traffic_Assignment\">Genetic Algorithms for Air Traffic Assignment</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ecai/ecai94.html\">ECAI 1994</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/m/Michalewicz:Zbigniew\">Zbigniew Michalewicz</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> (<b>1996</b>). <i>Evolutionary algorithms for constrained parameter optimization problems</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://cs.adelaide.edu.au/~zbyszek/Papers/p30.pdf\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2000_...\">2000 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2000 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/h/Hamida:Sana_Ben\">Sana Ben Hamida</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/3-540-45356-3_52\">An Adaptive Algorithm for Constrained Optimization Problems</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/db/conf/ppsn/ppsn2000.html\">PPSN 2000</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Aguston_E._Eiben&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Aguston E. Eiben (page does not exist)\">Aguston E. Eiben</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> (<b>2005</b>). <i>Evolutionary Computing</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/cs/0511004\">arXiv:cs/0511004</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Using Domain Knowledge in Evolutionary System Identification</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/cs/0602021\">arXiv:cs/0602021</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sylvain_Gelly\" title=\"Sylvain Gelly\">Sylvain Gelly</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicolas_Bred%C3%A8che&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nicolas Bredèche (page does not exist)\">Nicolas Bredèche</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> (<b>2006</b>). <i>Universal Consistency and Bloat in GP</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hal.inria.fr/inria-00112840/document\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nur_Merve_Amil&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nur Merve Amil (page does not exist)\">Nur Merve Amil</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Nicolas_Bred%C3%A8che&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Nicolas Bredèche (page does not exist)\">Nicolas Bredèche</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Christian_Gagn%C3%A9&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Christian Gagné (page does not exist)\">Christian Gagné</a>, <a href=\"/Sylvain_Gelly\" title=\"Sylvain Gelly\">Sylvain Gelly</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a> (<b>2009</b>). <i>A Statistical Learning Perspective of Genetic Programming</i>. EuroGP 2009, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hal.inria.fr/inria-00369782/document\">pdf</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2010_...\">2010 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2010 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://link.springer.com/chapter/10.1007/978-3-642-17298-4_24\">Dominance-Based Pareto-Surrogate for Multi-Objective Optimization</a></i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/seal/seal2010.html\">SEAL 2010</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hal.inria.fr/inria-00522653/document\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-7\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-7\">&#91;7&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2010</b>). <i>A mono surrogate for multiobjective optimization</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/gecco/gecco2010.html\">GECCO 2010</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://hal.inria.fr/inria-00483948/document\">pdf</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2011</b>). <i>Adaptive coordinate descent.</i> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.org/db/conf/gecco/gecco2011.html\">GECCO 2011</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.loshchilov.com/publications/GECCO2011_AdaptiveCoordinateDescent.pdf\">pdf</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-8\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-8\">&#91;8&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Sylvain_Gelly\" title=\"Sylvain Gelly\">Sylvain Gelly</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a>, <a href=\"/Levente_Kocsis\" title=\"Levente Kocsis\">Levente Kocsis</a>, <a href=\"/David_Silver\" title=\"David Silver\">David Silver</a>, <a href=\"/Csaba_Szepesv%C3%A1ri\" title=\"Csaba Szepesvári\">Csaba Szepesvári</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://dl.acm.org/citation.cfm?id=2093548.2093574\">The Grand Challenge of Computer Go: Monte Carlo Tree Search and Extensions</a></i>. <a href=\"/ACM#Communications\" title=\"ACM\">Communications of the ACM</a>, Vol. 55, No. 3, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www0.cs.ucl.ac.uk/staff/D.Silver/web/Applications_files/grand-challenge.pdf\">pdf preprint</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Self-Adaptive Surrogate-Assisted Covariance Matrix Adaptation Evolution Strategy</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1204.2356\">arXiv:1204.2356</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-9\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-9\">&#91;9&#93;</a></sup></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Alternative Restart Strategies for CMA-ES</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1207.0206\">arXiv:1207.0206</a> </li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Thomas_Philip_Runarsson\" title=\"Thomas Philip Runarsson\">Thomas Philip Runarsson</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2012</b>). <i>Pilot, Rollout and Monte Carlo Tree Search Methods for Job Shop Scheduling</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1210.0374\">arXiv:1210.0374</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Ilya_Loshchilov\" title=\"Ilya Loshchilov\">Ilya Loshchilov</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2013</b>). <i>KL-based Control of the Learning Schedule for Surrogate Black-Box Optimization</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1308.2655\">arXiv:1308.2655</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Olivier_Bousquet&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Olivier Bousquet (page does not exist)\">Olivier Bousquet</a>, <a href=\"/Sylvain_Gelly\" title=\"Sylvain Gelly\">Sylvain Gelly</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Karol_Kurach&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Karol Kurach (page does not exist)\">Karol Kurach</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a>, <a href=\"/Olivier_Teytaud\" title=\"Olivier Teytaud\">Olivier Teytaud</a>, <a href=\"/index.php?title=Damien_Vincent&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Damien Vincent (page does not exist)\">Damien Vincent</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Toward Optimal Run Racing: Application to Deep Learning Calibration</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1706.03199\">arXiv:1706.03199</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alice_Schoenauer-Sebag&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alice Schoenauer-Sebag (page does not exist)\">Alice Schoenauer-Sebag</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2017</b>). <i>Stochastic Gradient Descent: Going As Fast As Possible But Not Faster</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1709.01427\">arXiv:1709.01427</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Herilalaina_Rakotoarison&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Herilalaina Rakotoarison (page does not exist)\">Herilalaina Rakotoarison</a>, <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a>, <a href=\"/Mich%C3%A8le_Sebag\" title=\"Michèle Sebag\">Michèle Sebag</a> (<b>2019</b>). <i>Automated Machine Learning with Monte-Carlo Tree Search</i>. <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1906.00170\">arXiv:1906.00170</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.lri.fr/~marc/\">Home page of Marc Schoenauer, head of TAO team</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://genealogy.math.ndsu.nodak.edu/id.php?id=92800\">The Mathematics Genealogy Project - Marc Schoenauer</a></li>\n<li> <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Marc Schoenauer</a> - Full Interview, 2018, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/YouTube\">YouTube</a> Video</li></ul>\n<dl><dd> <div class='embedvideo ev_inline ev_top autoResize' style=' width: 646px;'><div class='embedvideowrap' style='width: 640px;'><iframe src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/7I0Sk8V_mz4?\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"true\"></iframe></div></div></dd></dl>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Marc_Schoenauer&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.lri.fr/~marc/\">Home page of Marc Schoenauer, head of TAO team</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://tao.lri.fr/tiki-index.php?page=People\">TikiWiki | People</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.lri.fr/%7Emarc/bio_short.html\">Short CV of Marc Schoenauer, Nov. 2008</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.lri.fr/~marc/selectedBib.html\">Marc Schoenauer - Selected Publications</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://dblp.uni-trier.de/pers/hd/s/Schoenauer:Marc\">dblp: Marc Schoenauer</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=GrCk6WoAAAAJ&amp;hl=en\">Marc Schoenauer - Google Scholar Citations</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Multi-objective_optimization\">Multi-objective optimization from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-8\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-8\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adaptive_coordinate_descent\">Adaptive coordinate descent from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-9\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CMA-ES\">CMA-ES from Wikipedia</a></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<p><b><a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">Up one level</a></b>\n</p>\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260301035043\nCache expiry: 86400\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.023 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.024 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 162/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 370/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 26/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 2/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key oscar70_mw1-mw_:pcache:idhash:6095-0!canonical and timestamp 20260301035043 and revision id 14290\n -->\n"
